---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-top">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <p class="footer-logo-main">小澤鶏卵</p>
        <p class="footer-logo-sub">OZAWA KEIRAN</p>
        <p class="footer-tagline">新鮮で安心なたまごを、毎日の食卓へ</p>
      </div>

      <nav class="footer-nav" aria-label="フッターナビゲーション">
        <div class="footer-nav-col">
          <p class="footer-nav-label">サイトマップ</p>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/">トップページ</a></li>
            <li><a href="/products">商品案内</a></li>
            <li><a href="/quality">品質へのこだわり</a></li>
            <li><a href="/company">会社概要</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">お問い合わせ</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-nav-col">
          <p class="footer-nav-label">お問い合わせ</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <a href="tel:0000-00-0000">TEL: 0000-00-0000</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="mailto:info@kozawa-keiran.com">info@kozawa-keiran.com</a>
            </li>
            <li class="footer-hours">
              <span>受付時間：月〜土 8:00〜17:00</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p class="copyright">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} 小澤鶏卵 All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    background-color: var(--color-dark-brown);
    color: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.75);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .footer-top {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.1);
  }

  .footer-logo-main {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-ivory);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .footer-logo-sub {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.45);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .footer-tagline {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.6);
  }

  .footer-nav {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-nav-label {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--color-egg-yellow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.625rem;
  }

  .footer-nav a {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.65);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .footer-nav a:hover {
    color: var(--color-ivory);
  }

  .footer-hours span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.45);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .copyright {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.35);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-top {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
    }

    .footer-nav {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .footer-nav {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
